    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">In a given setting with 23 people, the probability of at least two sharing a birthday is higher than 50%. So in the World Cup, where there are 32 teams with 23 players each, we can expect that there must be at least 16 teams with two or more players who share a birthday. According to a detailed study below, you will see that exactly 16 teams had players that shared a birthday.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
